# Routes
# This file defines all application routes (Higher priority routes first)
# ~~~~

# Home page
GET     /                                       SmsApplication.index

# 一号店API
*       /api/order/create                       OrderAPI.createOrder
*       /api/order/refund                       OrderAPI.refund
*       /api/order/resend                       OrderAPI.resend
